<h3 id="condensed-scale">Condensed Type Scale</h3>

<p>As you can see above, the standard Protocol type scale features big sizes for headings and titles appropriate for most general websites (like marketing sites, blogs, etc). Protocol also includes an alternative, condensed scale with smaller sizes more suitable for web applications.</p>

